                    Determine the area of rectangle <m>ILKO</m> with height <m>KL=6</m> cm.
                  </p>
                </statement>
              </task>
              <task>
                <statement>
                  <p>
                      Determine the area of right triangle <m>IJO</m>.
                  </p>
                </statement>
              </task>          
              <task>
                <statement>
                  <p>
